Kangaroo Cafe Tours for Ha Long Bay is the bomb!
There are thousands of tour companies in Hanoi and we had a hard time sorting out which tour to take to Ha Long Bay. A friend recommended Kangaoo Cafe tours (there are a bunch of fake ones, but the real one is on the west side of the lake. http://kangaroocafe.com/ ) We could not have been happier with them. Great crew, boat, etc. We did the 3 day trip and went kayaking, swimming, exploring and just hung out as well. (Ended up taking the Kangaroo Cafe trip to Sapa because they were so good.) The price was good too, you can pay less, but you end up on a big boat with 35 people. Ours was limited to 14 passengers. Best tour company we experienced in a month in Asia!
